{"_path":"/councilor/service/s4072","_dir":"service","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"現勘壽山路大貨車科技執法","description":null,"image":"/images/service/4072-1.jpeg","sequence":4072,"category1":"A. 健全都市發展","category2":"A.4 強化區域交通規劃","link":null,"author":"陳雅倫","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":"陳雅倫"},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-12-11T00:00:00.000Z","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"現勘壽山路大貨車科技執法"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"現勘壽山路大貨車科技執法"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"壽山路門架前些日子被撞壞，經聯繫新北市新莊區公所要到明年才能裝設～這段期間大貨車頻繁行駛陡峭蜿蜒的壽山路，顯得相當危險。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n因為壽山路僅有入口處屬於桃園轄區，雅倫趕緊來會勘設置大貨車科技執法，行經此路段的大貨車請留意自身的噸數喔！"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n另外雅倫也到文化一路、文明路會勘，希望在林口交流道立體化改善工程完工以前，先行加強路口淨空！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s40472-1.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s4072-1.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"現勘壽山路大貨車科技執法","depth":2,"text":"現勘壽山路大貨車科技執法"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:councilor:service:s4072.md","_source":"content","_file":"councilor/service/s4072.md","_extension":"md"}